    "summary": "Kensho exposes multiple authenticated developer surfaces: REST APIs for LLM-ready API, Scribe, NERD, Extract, and Adaptive Retrieval; streamable-http MCP servers for LLM-ready API and Adaptive Retrieval; plus a Python-packaged local kFinance MCP server CLI.",
